---
const today = new Date();
const name = 'Millie Qiu';
---

<footer>
  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="footer-title">
      <h3>讓一切從打招呼開始變得簡單</h3>
      <img src="../../public/wave.gif" alt="" />
    </div>
    <p>想提供工作機會或想與我交流任何想法，歡迎隨時聯繫 :)</p>
    <small>Email 📧 <a href="mailto:millie.yi110@gmail.com">millie.yi110@gmail.com</a></small>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-link">
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="https://www.behance.net/millieqiu-design" target="_blank"><img src="../../public/behance.png" alt=""></a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/qiumillie/" target="_blank"><img src="../../public/linkedin.png" alt=""></a>
      <a href="https://github.com/millieqiu" target="_blank"><img src="../../public/github.png" alt=""></a>
    </div>
    <small class="footer-copyright">
      &copy; {today.getFullYear()} {name}. All rights reserved.
    </small>
  </div>
</footer>
<style lang="scss">
  footer {
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background-color: white;
  }
  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--neutral-400);
    }
  }
  .footer-title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    img {
      max-width: 36px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      display: inline-block;
    }
  }
  .footer-link {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .footer-copyright {
    color: var(--neutral-400);
  }
  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1em;
    margin-top: 1em;
  }
  .social-links a {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    a, img {
      display: inline-block;
    }
    img {
      width: 2rem;
      transition:all 0.2s ease 0s;
    }
  }
  .social-links a:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    transition:all 0.2s ease 0s;
  }
</style>
